course.subject: COMP
course.name: Computer Engineering Final Year Project I
course.description: [Also ELEC 4905] Each Computer Engineering student is required to take COMP 4993, 4994 and 4995/ELEC 4905, 4915 and 4925. The project is conducted under the supervision of a faculty member of the Department of Computer Science and Engineering and/or Department of Electronic and Computer Engineering. May be graded PP.
